- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a family of trajectory tracking controllers for marine craft, which falls under the category of control systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): Although the paper is not specifically about robotics, the control techniques proposed could be applied to marine robots. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper involves numerical simulations to evaluate the performance of the proposed controllers. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): While the paper does not explicitly mention multiagent systems, the control techniques proposed could potentially be applied to coordinated control of multiple marine craft. 
- cs.OH (Other Computer Science): This category is a catch-all for papers that do not fit into any of the other categories. However, given the focus on control systems and numerical simulations, it seems likely that the paper would be classified under one of the other categories listed above.
